================================================================================
RENEWABLE ENERGY HARDWARE ENTERPRISE SYSTEM - CODE STRUCTURE
================================================================================

PROJECT OVERVIEW
================================================================================
This is a Java Swing desktop application for enterprise management of renewable
energy hardware businesses. It supports multi-role user access with separate
dashboards for Admin, Company Admin, Technician, and Customer roles.

Technologies:
- Java SE 11+
- Java Swing (GUI)
- H2 Database (Embedded, version 2.2.224)
- CSV Import/Export functionality

================================================================================
PROJECT STRUCTURE
================================================================================

Final Project/
├── app/
│   ├── Main.java                          # Application entry point
│   ├── IntroInterface.java                # Welcome/intro screen
│   ├── LoginFrame.java                    # Unified login for all user types
│   ├── DashboardFrame.java                # Admin dashboard
│   ├── CompanyAdminFrame.java             # Company Admin dashboard
│   ├── TechnicianFrame.java               # Technician dashboard
│   ├── CustomerPortal.java                # Customer portal
│   ├── DataStore.java                     # Data storage utilities
│   │
│   ├── abstracts/
│   │   ├── BaseUser.java                  # Abstract base class for all users
│   │   └── BaseFrame.java                 # Abstract base class for frames
│   │
│   ├── interfaces/
│   │   ├── Authenticatable.java           # Authentication interface
│   │   └── DataManageable.java            # CRUD operations interface
│   │
│   ├── model/
│   │   ├── Admin.java                     # Admin user model
│   │   ├── CompanyAdmin.java              # Company Admin user model
│   │   ├── Technician.java                # Technician user model
│   │   ├── Customer.java                  # Customer user model
│   │   ├── StockItem.java                 # Inventory item model
│   │   └── SupplierQuote.java             # Supplier quote model
│   │
│   └── util/
│       ├── DatabaseConnection.java        # Database connection singleton
│       ├── DatabaseInitializer.java       # Database schema initialization
│       ├── CSVUtil.java                   # CSV import/export utilities
│       ├── UIStyles.java                  # UI styling utilities
│       ├── UserManager.java               # User management utilities
│       │
│       ├── AdminDAO.java                   # Admin data access object
│       ├── CompanyAdminDAO.java           # Company Admin DAO
│       ├── TechnicianDAO.java             # Technician DAO
│       ├── CustomerDAO.java               # Customer DAO
│       ├── SalesOrderDAO.java             # Sales orders DAO
│       ├── InventoryDAO.java              # Inventory DAO
│       ├── SupplierDAO.java               # Suppliers DAO
│       ├── MaintenanceDAO.java            # Maintenance requests DAO
│       ├── StockRequestDAO.java           # Stock requests DAO
│       ├── StockArrivalDAO.java           # Stock arrivals DAO
│       ├── ScheduleDAO.java               # Schedules DAO
│       ├── TechnicianJobDAO.java          # Technician jobs DAO
│       ├── PartsRequestDAO.java           # Parts requests DAO
│       ├── TechnicianIssueDAO.java        # Technician issues DAO
│       └── CustomerIssueDAO.java          # Customer issues DAO
