================================================================================
FILE ORGANIZATION
================================================================================

Package Structure:
- app/                    - Main application classes
- app/abstracts/          - Abstract base classes
- app/interfaces/         - Interface definitions
- app/model/              - Data model classes
- app/util/               - Utility classes and DAOs

Design Patterns:
- Singleton: DatabaseConnection
- DAO Pattern: All *DAO.java classes
- MVC Pattern: Separation of Model, View, Controller
- Factory Pattern: User creation and authentication

